From a5c72afd2bc3e468f40c9298493a35814fd33c21 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: DeepAgent Bot <deepagent@research.ai>
Date: Sun, 21 Jun 2026 23:39:52 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Add DeepAgent Research OS frontend

A hybrid scientific-lab interface for orchestrating autonomous deep-research agents.

Features:
- Dashboard with real-time agent orchestration visualization
- New Research query composer with live pipeline monitoring
- Sessions management with filtering and detail views
- Reports library with rich markdown viewer
- Agent configuration and pipeline management
- Settings for API keys, defaults, and preferences

Tech stack: React + TypeScript + Vite + Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui
